wikipedia_page.main: Mariann Bienz FRS FMedSci is a distinguished molecular biologist based at the UK Medical Research Council Laboratory of Molecular Biology. She has been a member of their Senior Scientific Staff since 1991, was Joint-head of Cell Biology in 2007/8 and has been a Group Leader of Protein and Nucleic Acid Chemistry Division since 2008.
